<!-- okpack-competitive ships METHOD-ONLY: no feed list, because YOUR tracked market defines it.
     How to pick feeds (add to feeds.opml, not this file):
       1. Your market's trade press RSS (the 2-3 outlets that break vendor news first).
       2. Each tracked competitor's newsroom/blog RSS (press releases beat re-reporting).
       3. A funding/deals tracker for the segment (M&A + rounds are core `deal` signal).
       4. Regulator / standards-body feeds if your market is compliance-driven.
     Start with 5-10 feeds; more feeds = more noise for the ingest agent to filter. -->
